OL,3,CLord Blunkett injured after falling
OL,4,Cinto gap at tube station
OL,6,FLord Blunkett is calling for action on
OL,7,F"death trap" tube platforms after he
OL,8,Fwas injured falling into the gap at
OL,9,FWestminster station.
OL,11,FThe Labour peer, who is blind, called
OL,12,Fon Transport for London to do more to
OL,13,Fkeep visually impaired people safe.
OL,15,FHe was getting on a London Underground
OL,16,FDistrict Line train with his guide dog
OL,17,Fthree weeks ago when his feet slipped.
OL,19,F"As I took a step to get on to the
OL,20,Ftube train I suddenly felt both my
OL,21,Ffeet disappearing down the gap.
