OL,3,CLord Blunkett injured after falling
OL,4,Cinto gap at tube station
OL,6,F"In an instant my body had been
OL,7,Fpropelled forward into the carriage
OL,8,Fand I was face down on the floor.
OL,10,F"My legs had somehow been scraped out
OL,11,Fof the gap and into the carriage.
OL,13,F"I didn't fully know what had
OL,14,Fhappened. I felt enormous pain in both
OL,15,Fmy legs; they were bruised and
OL,16,Fgrazed," he wrote in the Sun on Sunday.
OL,18,FLord Blunkett's fall came after a
OL,19,Frecent heart attack that means he must
OL,20,Ftake blood thinners, which make any
OL,21,Fbruising or bleeding dangerous.
