OL,6,FAn X-ray confirmed "extraordinary
OL,7,Fbruising" but no broken leg, and he
OL,8,Fsays he is "angry" about what happened.
OL,10,F"Whenever you step into a tube station
OL,11,Fin London you hear the tannoy warn
OL,12,Fpeople to 'mind the gap'. But too
OL,13,Foften there are no staff members to
OL,14,Factually help you if, like me, you
OL,15,Fcannot see."
OL,17,FThe House of Lords member is calling
OL,18,Ffor TfL to make efforts to fill the
OL,19,Fwidest gaps on platforms and make sure
OL,20,Fthere is always someone there to help,
OL,21,Fespecially during rush hour.
