OL,3,CLord Blunkett injured after falling
OL,4,Cinto gap at tube station
OL,6,F"Some of our platforms are death
OL,7,Ftraps. The gap between the walkway and
OL,8,Ftrain is huge and they are unsafe for
OL,9,Feveryone, but particularly for blind
OL,10,Fpeople."
OL,12,FHe will soon meet TfL to ask for
OL,13,Fanswers and an urgent review into the
OL,14,Fsafety of the busiest tube stations.
OL,16,FNick Dent, London Underground's
OL,17,Fdirector of customer operations, said:
OL,18,F"We were extremely sorry that Lord
OL,19,FBlunkett was injured on our network.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]zD@AOU
