OL,3,CLord Blunkett injured after falling
OL,4,Cinto gap at tube station
OL,6,F"We have written to, and will be
OL,7,Fmeeting with, him to discuss how we
OL,8,Fcould have managed the incident better
OL,9,Fand to ensure that lessons are learned.
OL,11,F"The safety of our customers and staff
OL,12,Fis at the forefront of everything we
OL,13,Fdo, and while injuries like the one
OL,14,Fexperienced by Lord Blunkett are rare,
OL,15,Fwe are undertaking a huge range of
OL,16,Fwork aimed at eradicating such
OL,17,Fincidents and making travelling even
OL,18,Fsafer for everyone."
